headline: ICE’s Environmental Market Trading Reaches Record Highs in 2025
summary: AMSTERDAM & LONDON & NEW YORK, January 30, 2026--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE:ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data and the largest market in the world to trade environmental derivatives, today announced that 2025 was another record year for environmental trading on ICE.
